D. J. & T. SULLIVAN, Inc., Petitioner, v. David BURNET, Commissioner of Internal Revenue, Respondent. No. 6453. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 1, 1931.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of respondent, or-. dered petition to review in above cause dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
